{"tid":757947,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DAB區議員疑趕絕水池蝌蚪 街坊代蛙發聲貼圖抗議：我會返嚟架","createTime":"2018-07-27T09:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T10:40:45.000Z","uid":70063,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"507bb47c77cbb3e75e5878bbf7869706f34d9fd2","tid":757947,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180727/large/1532672111_6521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180727%2Flarge%2F1532672111_6521.jpg&h=13bbcb38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民建聯元朗區議員馬淑燕日前在其facebook發帖指，天耀邨水池生長不少蝌蚪，恐怕變成青蛙後叫聲擾民，要求邨管公司能妥善並盡快處理，惹來大批網民批評。有居民前日更發現有清潔人員在水池撈捕東西，疑是「殺蝌」行動，馬淑燕事後稱沒有要求殺任合生物，只想將漁池變成一個生態池。不過，近日有街坊疑不滿馬淑燕提出的要求，在其辦事處外貼寫上「我會返嚟架！」的青蛙惡搞圖，「代蛙發聲」抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180727/small/1532670764_d915.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180727%2Fsmall%2F1532670764_d915.jpg&h=eadb2877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180727/small/1532670759_afd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180727%2Fsmall%2F1532670759_afd1.jpg&h=54511696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據街坊提供圖片，總共有兩張網上惡搞常用的「青蛙圖」，其中一張加上「我甚麼都不是」字句，另一張青蛙流淚圖充滿怨氣，寫有「我會返嚟架」字句。<br />\n<br />\n馬淑燕本周三曾在fb再發帖解畫，指有很多網民和媒體關注天耀邨水池的蝌蚪，她指早年天耀邨的水池內是有魚、龜等可愛小動物，可供居民觀賞，但多年前因為管理問題，令到水池開始荒廢無水，「近日水池重新放水後，有本區居民向我反映，水池有很多蝌蚪出現，擔心單一的物種會影響水池生態的多樣性，以及日後有機會對居民的影響」。她稱感謝大家的關注和寶貴意見，會虛心受教，繼續跟進水池的情況。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者日前到天耀邨視察，有居民指間中會聽到疑似青蛙叫聲，但未至於擾民，認為不需要將蝌蚪趕盡殺絕，控制數量便可；另有居民認為水池塘最好有動物。漁護署日前表示，已主動向相關邨管了解情況，提醒法例對保護野生動物的要求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180727/58492689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180727%2F58492689&d=JmNU5v9Q9H3OZc%2Fqpm0n7%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=b57c8db6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180727%2F58492689&h=9a277bcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180727/58492689</a>"},{"pid":"d5ac2111577afcace939c618b22657dd0e3cc36e","tid":757947,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:10:10.000Z","msg":"毒撚蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77150ce9b7e0a6ffab5e22ea581594e42b9af8f7","tid":757947,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:24:06.000Z","msg":"成件事灰階咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c370fba266cd54f75e69b0d51a57d3eb8ab662c6","tid":757947,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79929d3a296a970c645aba2170a604fe8be6a372","tid":757947,"uid":41602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:28:46.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打傑作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a935b0df5086dc3a46fef5f85e3dff6083221a1","tid":757947,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:32:51.000Z","msg":"pepehands<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28114bcd00b136a69494f2b076643fafd93bf6a7","tid":757947,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T10:37:18.000Z","msg":"其實養幾條錦鯉應該就OK，係要做得咁肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4ec88fabc37cfb03a57eddb51d23ed68599e5d","tid":757947,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"係咪唔知直寫要右至左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji